            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Deisan</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> domo <lb n="2"/>Hemesa ve&amp;lt;t=I&amp;gt;(eranus) &amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;x s&amp;lt;ta&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>tor</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I |(miliariae) H&amp;lt;e=P&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>esenorum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>vivus sibi &amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;&amp;lt;t&amp;gt; viv&amp;lt;en=M&amp;gt;<lb break="no" n="4"/>tibus Aureli<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>Monimo <expan><abbr>strat</abbr><ex>ori</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et Regi&amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;iano li&amp;lt;b=D&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ario</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>l&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ieg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>posuit <lb n="9"/>et <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Abigeneo <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ui</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ixit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XVII <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>enses</ex></expan> X &amp;lt;d&amp;gt;(ies)<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> XVII <lb n="10"/>et <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Prisciano m&amp;lt;il=R&amp;gt;(iti) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> nepotibu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Maße beziehen sich auf den Sarkophagkasten; Maße des Deckels: 53 x 250 x 130 cm. Zu beiden Seiten des Inschriftfeldes je eine männliche Figur. Z. 1: N in Deisan nicht ganz sicher zu lesen. Z. 4 (Anfang): T nachträglich aus R verbessert. Z. 9 (Ende): MXXVII nachträglich auf den Rahmen geschrieben. (B): CIL III; Lőrincz: Abweichungen in der Lesung. Fundort unklar: Dunaújváros (CIL), Adony (Mahler, vgl. Erdélyi - Fülep), Rácalmás (Erdélyi - Fülep).</p>
            </div>
